---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Us | Engineering Firm in Pasadena, Maryland | FirstLayer Digital"
	description="Maryland-based computer systems design practice specializing in operational infrastructure, internal tools, data dashboards (Streamlit), private cloud solutions (Proxmox, Nextcloud), and custom business infrastructure."
>
	<main role="main">

		<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
			<!-- Hero -->
			<div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20">
				<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
					Versatile Solutions, <span class="text-[var(--accent-cyan)] drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(34,211,238,0.3)]">Engineered</span> for Growth
				</h1>
				<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[var(--text-body)] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					We bridge the gap between custom engineering and operational infrastructure. From data dashboards and private cloud deployments to high-speed websites and e-commerce platforms, we build the tools your business needs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-10 items-start mb-16 sm:mb-20">
				<!-- Left: Engineer's Advantage -->
				<div class="bg-[var(--bg-card)] border border-[var(--stroke)] rounded-lg p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-header)] mb-4">The Engineer's Advantage</h2>
					<p class="text-[var(--text-body)] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
						Many agencies are limited to one tool. At FirstLayer Digital, we take a Computer Science approach to the entire web ecosystem. We don't just drag and drop; we configure, optimize, and engineer solutions that fit <em class="text-[var(--text-header)]">your</em> specific business needs.
					</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--text-body)] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
						We specialize in <strong class="text-[var(--text-header)]">Operational Infrastructure</strong> including Data Dashboards (Streamlit), Private Cloud solutions (Proxmox, Nextcloud), and Internal Tools development. We also build complex E-commerce environments, configure Inventory Management systems, and create Professional Portfolios that stand out.
					</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--text-body)] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
						Photo, video, and text editing services are standard services we perform as part of most website development projects, ensuring your content looks polished and professional.
					</p>
					<p class="text-[var(--text-body)] leading-relaxed font-medium">
						Already have a site? We can optimize it. Need something new? We can build it. We bring technical precision to every platform we touch.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Right: Platforms & Services -->
				<div class="bg-[var(--bg-card)] border border-[var(--stroke)] rounded-lg p-6 sm:p-8">
					<h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-header)] mb-4 text-lg">Platforms We Work With</h3>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text-body)] mb-6">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>WordPress</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Shopify</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Astro / Custom</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Wix</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Squarespace</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Weebly</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Square</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--accent)] rounded-full"></span>Others on Request</div>
					</div>

					<h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-header)] mb-3 border-t border-[var(--stroke)] pt-5 text-lg">Core Services</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--text-body)] mb-6">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>E-commerce & Inventory Setup</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>SEO & Performance Optimization</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>Data Dashboards (Streamlit)</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>Private Cloud (Proxmox)</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>Internal Tools & Automation</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>Photo, Video & Content Editing</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--accent)] mt-0.5 font-bold">&check;</span>Portfolio & Personal Branding</li>
					</ul>

					<h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-header)] mb-3 border-t border-[var(--stroke)] pt-5 text-lg">Engagement Model</h3>
					<div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--text-body)]">
						<div class="bg-[var(--bg-muted)] rounded-md p-3 border border-[var(--stroke)]">
							<strong class="text-[var(--text-header)]">Phase 1:</strong> $0 Credited Consultation &mdash; requirements mapping, credited toward final cost.
						</div>
						<div class="bg-[var(--bg-muted)] rounded-md p-3 border border-[var(--stroke)]">
							<strong class="text-[var(--text-header)]">Phase 2:</strong> Fixed-Price MVP &mdash; predictable pricing, clear deliverables, 60-day support.
						</div>
						<div class="bg-[var(--bg-muted)] rounded-md p-3 border border-[var(--stroke)]">
							<strong class="text-[var(--text-header)]">Phase 3:</strong> Hourly Scaling &mdash; ongoing enhancements and maintenance beyond MVP.
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- CTA -->
			<section class="text-center border-t border-[var(--stroke)] pt-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Build Something Together</h2>
				<p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-[var(--text-body)] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					Ready to talk about your project? We'd love to hear what you're working on.
				</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-[var(--accent)] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-[var(--accent-hover)] transition-colors duration-200 min-h-[48px]">
					Start a Conversation
				</a>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
